title: War of the Roses: They Facetime at 10:30PM?
description: Connie was out shoveling and walked into her house to see her boyfriend Facetiming with a girl that Connie goes to the gym with.  She thought that was weird so she did some digging to find out if this was a regular thing.  It apparently is and now Connie is wondering what they could possibly be Facetiming about, plus we throw in a little twist when we call him this time!
